title: Mexico Domestic Car Sales
description: Car Registrations in Mexico decreased to 36951 in October from 37959 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Mexico averaged 47106.16  from 1988 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 127604  in December of 2016 and a record low of 6318  in April of 1995. This page provides - Mexico Domestic Car Sales - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Instituto Nacional de Estadística y Geografía (INEGI)
